sentences: The band begun making music and performing locally in 2003.
After signing a record deal with Blood and Ink Records in 2007, several nationwide tours and two studio albums, the group officially disbanded in 2009.

The band commenced as a musical entity in 2003.
Their first release was an extended play entitled Set Our Hearts to Burn, which was released independently by the band on December 13, 2006.
Their first studio album Hope for the Best, Prepare for the Worst was released by Blood and Ink Records on May 8, 2007.
The subsequent release Brutus was also released with Blood and Ink Records on July 15, 2008.
